      "cookedHtml": "<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/rocket.png?v=12\" title=\":rocket:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":rocket:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> We’ve developed an amazing scenario in <a href=\"http://Make.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Make.com</a> that revolutionizes how we manage deals from ZohoSalesIQ conversations! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/speech_balloon.png?v=12\" title=\":speech_balloon:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":speech_balloon:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/arrow_right.png?v=12\" title=\":arrow_right:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":arrow_right:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/briefcase.png?v=12\" title=\":briefcase:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":briefcase:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/mag.png?v=12\" title=\":mag:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":mag:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Here’s how it works:</p>\n<p>1)Monitor ZohoSalesIQ Conversations <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/man_detective.png?v=12\" title=\":man_detective:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":man_detective:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>2)Search for Client in <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a> using email <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/mag_right.png?v=12\" title=\":mag_right:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":mag_right:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/e-mail.png?v=12\" title=\":e-mail:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":e-mail:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>3)If no client is found, create a new client in the Client Board <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/new.png?v=12\" title=\":new:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":new:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/busts_in_silhouette.png?v=12\" title=\":busts_in_silhouette:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":busts_in_silhouette:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>4)Retrieve Conversation Details using ZohoSalesIQ’s “Get a Conversation” module <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/card_index_dividers.png?v=12\" title=\":card_index_dividers:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":card_index_dividers:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/page_facing_up.png?v=12\" title=\":page_facing_up:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":page_facing_up:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>5)Aggregate Text Messages for comprehensive context <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/memo.png?v=12\" title=\":memo:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":memo:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>6)Search the Client Board again using the email <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/mag.png?v=12\" title=\":mag:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":mag:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/e-mail.png?v=12\" title=\":e-mail:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":e-mail:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>7)Create a Deal in the Deal Board with all client details and requirements! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/briefcase.png?v=12\" title=\":briefcase:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":briefcase:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/handshake.png?v=12\" title=\":handshake:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":handshake:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>This automation ensures  client management and deal creation, boosting efficiency and accuracy. <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/trophy.png?v=12\" title=\":trophy:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":trophy:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/sparkles.png?v=12\" title=\":sparkles:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":sparkles:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/globe_with_meridians.png?v=12\" title=\":globe_with_meridians:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":globe_with_meridians:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Let’s transform the way we handle conversations and deals! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/rocket.png?v=12\" title=\":rocket:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":rocket:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/sparkles.png?v=12\" title=\":sparkles:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":sparkles:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/6/4/64232e90d9cfbd7f58599b507b76b76a2150ae2f.png\" title=\"image (15)\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/6/4/64232e90d9cfbd7f58599b507b76b76a2150ae2f_2_690x337.png\" alt=\"image (15)\" width=\"690\" height=\"337\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image (15)</span><span class=\"informations\">1821×891 80.1 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>If you require additional assistance, please don’t hesitate to reach out to us.<br />\n<a href=\"https://calendly.com/msquarepro/meeting\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">MSquare Support</a> | <a href=\"https://calendly.com/msquarepro/msquareautomation-live\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Book Live Implementation</a><br />\nVisit us <a href=\"https://www.msquare.pro/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">here</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCqidlIIwbejxZmRUWBICcjQ\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Youtube Channel</a></p>"
